ess key ecological questions with biodiversity monitoring. We hope that our\nreproducible workflow will be useful to ecologists and applied statisticians.\n  All material (source of the Rmarkdown notebook and auxiliary files) is\navailable from\nhttps://github.com/oliviergimenez/computo-deeplearning-occupany-lynx.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Aug 2021 22:56:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-27"}
