ming improves knowledge about the architecture. Furthermore, we show\nthat with increased knowledge about the control architecture of the robot,\nusers were significantly better in reaching the interaction goal. Furthermore,\nwe showed that anthropomorphism may reduce interaction success.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 07:04:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-27"}
