RI and abdominal organs segmentation for CT) to demonstrate the\nstate-of-the-art performance and broad applicability of the proposed framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 10:24:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 Oct 2021 03:01:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
