mber of\ndiscretized bins, and diffusion parameter. This demonstrates the ability to\nproduce flux limiters that should be more broadly useful than standard limiters\nfor general applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 15:41:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 12:09:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 02:16:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
